ss=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.qaa.ac.uk/AboutUs/corporate/Documents/BACMoASept09.pdf\">\"Memorandum of Agreement concerning the collection and use of information\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. Qaa.ac.uk<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-03-05</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Memorandum+of+Agreement+concerning+the+collection+and+use+of+information&amp;rft.pub=Qaa.ac.uk&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.qaa.ac.uk%2FAboutUs%2Fcorporate%2FDocuments%2FBACMoASept09.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABritish+Accreditation+Council\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20130604110757/http://www.britishcouncil.org/accreditation-about-us-asac.htm\">\"ASAC - About us - British Council - Accreditation\"</a>. British Council. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.britishcouncil.org/accreditation-about-us-asac.htm\">the original</a> on 4 June 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2013-08-17</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=ASAC+-+About+us+-+British+Council+-+Accreditation&amp;rft.pub=British+Council&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.britishcouncil.org%2Faccreditation-about-us-asac.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABritish+Accreditation+Council\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.awarding.org.uk/fab-stakeholders/bac-british-accreditation-council\">\"Bac British Accreditation Council &#124; Fab Stakeholders\"</a>. Awarding.org.uk<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2013-08-17</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Bac+British+Accreditation+Council+%26%23124%3B+Fab+Stakeholders&amp;rft.pub=Awarding.org.uk&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.awarding.org.uk%2Ffab-stakeholders%2Fbac-british-accreditation-council&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABritish+Accreditation+Council\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-charity-commission1-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-charity-commission1_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20100917103905/http://www.charity-commission.gov.uk/Showcharity/RegisterOfCharities/CharityFramework.aspx?RegisteredCharityNumber=326652&amp;SubsidiaryNumber=0\">[1]</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Matthews, David (2012-04-05). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?storycode=419525\">\"College principal cheated Herts and students &#124; General\"</a>. Times Higher Education<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2013-08-17</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=College+principal+cheated+Herts+and+students+%26%23124%3B+General&amp;rft.pub=Times+Higher+Education&amp;rft.date=2012-04-05&amp;rft.aulast=Matthews&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeshighereducation.co.uk%2Fstory.asp%3Fstorycode%3D419525&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABritish+Accreditation+Council\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201011/cmselect/cmbis/writev/885/m60.htm\">\"The Future of Higher Education (13th July 2011)\"</a>. Publications.parliament.uk<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2013-08-17</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Future+of+Higher+Education+%2813th+July+2011%29&amp;rft.pub=Publications.parliament.uk&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fpublications.parliament.uk%2Fpa%2Fcm201011%2Fcmselect%2Fcmbis%2Fwritev%2F885%2Fm60.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABritish+Accreditation+Council\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20100506144903/http://www.britishcouncil.org/kosovo-projects-setting-standards-in-higher-education-2.htm\">\"Our work in education and society\"</a>. British Council. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.britishcouncil.org/kosovo-projects-setting-standards-in-higher-education-2.htm\">the original</a> on 2010-05-06<span clas